lyrics:
[verse]
In the black of night, where fright takes hold
Creatures lurking, secrets to unfold
Haunted animatronics, shadows arise
A haunting melody, sending shivers down my spine

[chorus]
Five Nights at Freddy's, a nightmare come true
Survive the horrors, they're after you
Lock the doors, keep your flashlight bright
Beware the animatronics, they'll haunt you tonight
